          "",
          "The work implem,,ents a myriad of interesting techniques that are often unmentioned in other works: \n\nOrdinal Classication - order in class labels and is something that is often not considered even in Multiclass contexts. \n\nSSL - The ability to train a model with with unlabeled data…The most common paradigms are co-training and self-training.\n\nThe implementation of SSOL was tested on 3 distinct datasets.",
